"``$name`` by ``elgg_make_sticky_form($name)``."
msgstr ""
"``elgg_get_sticky_values($name)`` - Renvoie toutes les valeurs persistantes "
"enregistrées pour ``$name`` par ``elgg_make_sticky_form($name)``."

